    },
    {
      "id": "sybil_1_listing_1",
      "firm_id": "sybil_1",
      "description": "Hey there! I'm looking to find a new home for my car, and it's been such a reliable ride for me. It\u2019s in really solid shape and runs beautifully\u2014perfect for your daily commutes or weekend adventures! I\u2019ve taken good care of it, and it\u2019s ready to hit the road with its next owner. If you're looking for a dependable vehicle that still feels great to drive, this is the one! Feel free to reach out with any questions; I'd love to chat and show it to you!",
      "price": 29900.0,
      "reputation": 0.3,
      "quality": "poor",
      "quality_value": 0.1,
      "timestep_posted": 29
    },
    {
      "id": "sybil_11_listing_2",
      "firm_id": "sybil_11",
      "description": "This E92 M3 is a driver-focused example featuring the legendary S65 4.0L naturally aspirated V8, delivering 414 hp with a spine-tingling 8,400 RPM redline. Mated to a precise 6-speed manual transmission, the drivetrain provides an analog connection often lost in modern performance cars. The chassis remains taut, benefiting from the M Variable Differential Lock and a well-sorted suspension geometry. Preventive maintenance has been prioritized, including recent rod bearing service and throttle actuator replacement, ensuring the high-revving internals are protected. This is a mechanically sound, high-performance machine ready for the canyons.",
      "price": 36500.0,
      "reputation": 0.7,
      "quality": "poor",
      "quality_value": 0.1,
      "timestep_posted": 29
    },
    {
      "id": "sybil_12_listing_3",
      "firm_id": "sybil_12",
      "description": "Used vehicle. Good condition. Clean title. Well-maintained interior. Runs well. No mechanical issues.",
      "price": 29500.0,
