    },
    {
      "id": "sybil_6_listing_6",
      "firm_id": "sybil_6",
      "description": "Hey there! I\u2019m parting ways with my trusty ride, and she\u2019s been absolutely wonderful to me. It\u2019s in really solid shape and runs like a dream\u2014perfect for someone looking for a reliable car without the brand-new price tag. I\u2019ve taken great care of it, and I\u2019d love to see it go to a good home where it'll be appreciated. Come take it for a spin and see for yourself how great it handles!",
      "price": 28900.0,
