    },
    {
      "id": "sybil_13_listing_7",
      "firm_id": "sybil_13",
      "description": "Available is a mechanically sound E46 M3, featuring the iconic S54 3.2L inline-six with its 8,000 RPM redline and individual throttle bodies. This example retains its crisp 6-speed Getrag manual transmission and factory limited-slip differential. The VANOS system has been serviced, and the rear subframe has been proactively inspected for structural integrity. Riding on a refreshed suspension with poly bushings for sharpened turn-in, this chassis offers the tactile feedback and linear power delivery enthusiasts demand. While showing minor aesthetic patina consistent with its driver status, the drivetrain remains robust and track-ready.",
